      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i really hope it is just stress. it hurts more when i take a deep breath though, like a sharp stabbing feeling. do u think i should wait it out for a few hours to see if it goes away or should i actually go to the hospital right now? i dont wanna make a big deal out of nothing if it's just a panic attack.",
