      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm kinda scared of hospitals tbh. plus i have a huge meeting in a couple hours and i really can't miss it. do u think i could just take some ibuprofen or maybe an antacid and see if it settles down first? i'm sure it's just indigestion or something from the airplane food.",
